# Apalache counterexample dump directory.
#
# The nightly formal-tla-liveness lane (M03.P3.T4) writes raw Apalache
# counterexample traces here when RevocationEventuallySeen (or any of
# the safety invariants) fails. Filed issues use the templates under
# formal/issue-templates/ and link the trace by relative path.
#
# Naming convention:
#   <PropertyName>-<UTC-date>-<short-sha>.txt
# for example:
#   RevocationEventuallySeen-2026-05-01-abc1234.txt
#
# This .gitkeep exists so the directory is tracked even when no
# counterexamples are filed. Do not delete.
